OL,3,CPrince William to join Aston Villa
OL,4,Cfans in Turkey for Europa League final
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales will travel to
OL,7,FTurkey to watch his team Aston Villa
OL,8,Ftake on Freiburg in the Europa League
OL,9,Ffinal on Wednesday (20 May).
OL,11,FIt will be the first time the club
OL,12,Fhave reached a major European final
OL,13,Fsince May 1982, their 1-0 victory over
OL,14,FBayern Munich in Rotterdam was just
OL,15,Fless than a month after William was
OL,16,Fborn.
