OL,3,CPrince William to join Aston Villa
OL,4,Cfans in Turkey for Europa League final
OL,6,FWilliam told comedian Matt Lucas that
OL,7,Fhe would be at the game in Istanbul
OL,8,Fafter Lucas received an OBE for
OL,9,Fservices to drama at Windsor Castle on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,FLucas, 52, said: "I asked him about
OL,13,Ffootball and whether he would be able
OL,14,Fto get to the cup final tomorrow that
OL,15,FAston Villa are playing in, and he
OL,16,Fsaid he can.
OL,18,F"He asked me what I was up to work
OL,19,Fwise and said some kind things about
OL,20,Fmy work."
OL,26,@tD@ROUzD@AOU|D@IO]
