OL,3,CPrince William to join Aston Villa
OL,4,Cfans in Turkey for Europa League final
OL,6,FWilliam has been a fan of the team
OL,7,Fsince he was a schoolboy and is also a
OL,8,Fpatron of the Football Association.
OL,10,FThe prince was photographed cheering
OL,11,Ffrom the stands during the team's 4-0
OL,12,Fwin against Nottingham Forest on 7 May
OL,13,Fwhich secured them a 4-1 aggregate win.
OL,15,FHe also later celebrated with players
OL,16,Fin the dressing room after their
OL,17,Fvictory.
OL,19,FAston Villa manager Unai Emery
OL,20,Fconfirmed William had joined in with
OL,21,Fpost-match celebrations.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
